HEADWORD: Refectory
<hw>Re*fec"to*ry</hw> <pr>(-⟦osl⟧*r⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it>; <plw>Refectories</plw> <pr>(-r<?/z)</pr>.</plu>
